tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits. HbA1c is at the upper limit of normal, suggesting good glycemic control but close monitoring is advised. Renal function, electrolytes, and metabolic parameters are unremarkable. No acute laboratory abnormalities detected.
